         I don't care how much effort it requires.. if the stats aren't worth that much money to me, the item is too expensive. Now maybe it's not too expensive for other people, but to me it is.</P><P>I refuse to pay that much money for what's basically +5 to saves and 55hp/mana (I don't even consider int as a stat anymore, high end items have so much int it's pointless to worry about it).</P><P>And I've done the FT debate before.. I think FT is stupid unless you can get it in large quantities.</P><P><a href="http://tru7h.org/absor/" target="_blank">http://tru7h.org/absor/</a> -  ask absor anything!<BR><a href="http://xzzy.org/ereet/" target="_blank">http://xzzy.org/ereet/</a><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
