        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         So say you don't get this earring. Here are your choices for better and worse (not 100% up to date, but only thing allakhazams doesn't usually list is stuff most people have no chance at getting anyway, and aren't listed because the people that do get them don't care enough to post them):<BR>Iron cogg earring ac10 str5 hp100... good luck finding someone selling this<BR>Singed Petrified Leaf: ac 7 str 10 sta/dex/wis/int/cold 5 magic 15 pos 10 hp/mana 70... drops from creator, very obtainable by most raiding guilds<BR>Solist's Earring of Insight: ac 25 int 15 svs 4 90 hp... drops off vulak, need I say more?<BR>Lizard Bone Earring: ac 2 sta 10 agi/dex 6 cha/posion/disease 5 hp 70 mana 35...another obtainable one by anyone that can find a decent group and puts hours into farming it, or buys it<BR>Hammered Golden Loop: ac-15 sta 7 magic 5 hp 75...very obtainable again<BR>Earring of the solstice: you know the stats...buyable on all servers I assume, so obtainable by everyone with a wallet</P><P>I'd rate this earring as (going by what allakhazam's has listed) one of the top 3 earrings for people who aren't AE manaburning the ring of vulak to get his earrings. 30k for something that touches so high on the charts isn't unreasonable at all.</P><P>Copied and pasted for your viewing pleasure in the correct topic~</P><P><BR> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
