         FT is nice in large quantites yes. But keep in mind you are adding ft1 to the ear slot. Most items with FT on it are..Head,Face,Boots,Neck, and or Range..Robe as well. So later on down the line if you loot thoose items that  FT1 you have in your ear will be nice. As far as the Shadel Bandit ring yes the stats are near the same...but once again we are talking about the ear slot..not the finger slot. It is costly and if a person cannot afford it then by all means the hp 25/mana 35 earings are excellant. Hell up to lvl 60 and 30+ aa points thats all I used. </P><P>Ibudin</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
